  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375° F (190° C).",
    "Cut the boudin-blanc into 1-inch cubes.",
    "In a large skillet, sauté the mirepoix base over medium heat until tender.",
    "In a greased 9x13-inch baking dish, arrange half of the boudin-blanc cubes.",
    "Spread half of the mirepoix base mixture over the boudin-blanc.",
    "Repeat the layers, starting with the remaining boudin-blanc, then the remaining mirepoix base mixture.",
